commit.message: - Addressed review comments.
Remove Resolve minimum delay and a couple other tiny fixes
Improvements to the correction details dialog box
Fixed improper formatting in ARGYLL_COLPROF_ARGS and ARGYLL_DISPCAL_ARGS
Adds checks so the matrix graph will still draw even if the .ccmx does not contain certain values
Sets a minimum size for the matrix window, otherwise it spawns as the full width of the display and can't be resized
Temp fix to put the name of a virtual display into the dialog box
Spectrometer reading is fixed to correctly save as the reference, not as the colorimeter
Add i1 Pro 3 to the list so that is it recognized as a spectrometer
